{"tid":756824,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"犯罪學家：離世前最後溫存","createTime":"2018-07-26T10:11:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-26T11:39:59.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"54e98509447d8ab7b5137fef2b6862dbdd0975df","tid":756824,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T10:11:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180726/20460553\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180726%2F20460553&d=7Xr0jXPxAHzVd%2F645HDZxZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=816dbce5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180726%2F20460553&h=998913b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180726/20460553</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年07月26日 <br />\n<br />\n犯罪學家：離世前最後溫存<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180726/large/26la1p4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180726%2Flarge%2F26la1p4.jpg&h=4838453f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■大批警員在發生雙屍案的昇御門調查。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】紅磡雙屍案中兩死者為情侶，死因有待驗屍確認，案中謎團亦有待警方調查。城大犯罪學家黎定基稱不排除案件涉及自殺殉情，或是一宗謀殺及自殺案。黎指自殺不外乎為情或為債，如雙方在感情上受衝擊，覺得問題無法解決，遂結盟同年同月同日死。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n或受酒精藥物影響<br />\n<br />\n至於兩人下身赤裸，黎相信雙方有很深厚的感情或糾紛牽涉其中，不排除有人在離開世界之前作最後一次親密行為。<br />\n<br />\n黎認為現階段難以分析案件背後原因及動機，尋死可以是一時衝動的念頭，但總有萌芽階段，此階段可長可短。一旦事主曾飲酒或服藥，有機會在受酒精及藥物影響下以死解決問題。而謀殺及自殺案的事主，通常抱有單方面希望與對方同死的心態，故先殺死對方，然後自殺。<br />\n<br />\n其實過去亦有發生涉及情殺的案件，去年3月16日，一名28歲女子在大埔富亨邨被發現全裸昏迷床上，後腦及四肢有傷痕，送院不治，其懷疑不滿戴綠帽施襲的42歲同居男友被控謀殺罪，但法醫認為死者死因其實與毒品有關，被告獲改控襲擊傷人，認罪判監一年。<br />\n<br />\n2016年8月6日，一對正辦離婚手續的夫婦因感情爭執，60歲丈夫在土瓜灣住所疑殺害41歲妻子後，畏罪跳海自殺獲救，其後丈夫被落案控以一項謀殺罪上庭。<br />\n<br />\n■記者張珮琪  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n與母投資貝沙灣賺多蝕少<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n與母投資貝沙灣賺多蝕少<br />\n<br />\n作家倒斃豪宅　女友死床上兩人下身赤裸　同現屍斑"},{"pid":"657441db4e34ef3243709a548d5aa96253bf316d","tid":756824,"uid":35712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T10:15:19.000Z","msg":"姦屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"238de5ca13818b999864511d0638d4a89bf69a94","tid":756824,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"657441db4e34ef3243709a548d5aa96253bf316d","tid":756824,"uid":35712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T10:15:19.000Z","msg":"姦屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T10:20:03.000Z","msg":"識諗就係呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4b45e25825c9bb9ba2a0b8031bcbd918a5a3dbf","tid":756824,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"238de5ca13818b999864511d0638d4a89bf69a94","tid":756824,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"657441db4e34ef3243709a548d5aa96253bf316d","tid":756824,"uid":35712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T10:15:19.000Z","msg":"姦屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T10:20:03.000Z","msg":"識諗就係呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T